{"tid":1614020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日一戰證明左呢個戰術好成功","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:04:41.000Z","uid":76364,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"abece395c2a62ab097ef87f2204bb5c5e079a7ba","tid":1614020,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"班popo諗住大家休息<br />\n邊估到大家幾個鐘前吹雞，仲要有咁多人響應，搞到佢地措手不及<br />\n諗住六日完左可以好好休息，但佢地邊撚到估到連平日都要出動<br />\n人地得三萬咁多，但我地係佢地好幾十倍，人數上絕對優勢<br />\n好希望大家都可以堅持，就算一日半日唔得都仲可以靠其他人接力，到得閒就輪到自己上場，等其他人休息<br />\n咁樣黎消耗戰不失為一個好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b265cddd79f84397915c5aeb7572ca4200608b78","tid":1614020,"uid":152584,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"平日一至五要隨機抽兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd729d2ca6050ea513d2c1cdabbaade0046c1fd2","tid":1614020,"uid":66221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"打紅色企業店鋪絕對安全過圍狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545a08680f5bde53323ca40377b88f48bf77448d","tid":1614020,"uid":212182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"平日聚到人，絕對可以搞死佢地"},{"pid":"50ca5b45a7a46c2c744cd3943d422d598d3a625f","tid":1614020,"uid":311275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc2290df9530b1fbb22282c41e11a1dff46fe67","tid":1614020,"uid":169079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cd729d2ca6050ea513d2c1cdabbaade0046c1fd2","tid":1614020,"uid":66221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"打紅色企業店鋪絕對安全過圍狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"h